title: Science Fiction Magazines Battle a Flood of Chatbot-Generated Stories
description: While the deluge has become a nuisance, the stories are easy to spot. The writing is “bad in spectacular ways,” one editor said.

title: Why You Should Listen to Twitter on Two-Factor Authentication
description: Elon Musk was right: Text messages are not the most secure way to protect your account.

title: Chip Makers Turn Cutthroat in Fight for Share of Federal Money
description: Semiconductor companies, which united to get the CHIPS Act approved, have set off a lobbying frenzy as they argue for more cash than their competitors.
